											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="[Player - Astarion] bares his fangs, lowering himself to [Pandirna's] level. He grabs her head, pulling it sideways to better expose her neck. He lunges at her neck, biting down hard and violently. We see the life draining from [Pandirna] as her struggling slows before stopping and her body going limp. [Astarion] lets go, stumbling backwards, satisfied from feeding. He takes a moment before standing back up. - Matt" />
